<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 15:15:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>上海证券交易所延迟交易后进行测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shanghai-stock-exchange-run-test-after-transaction-delay-2024-09-28/</link><description>据国营《证券时报》周六报道，中国上海证券交易所将于周日对其拍卖平台和其他多个平台进行测试，一天前，交易发生了不明原因的延迟。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 11:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shanghai-stock-exchange-run-test-after-transaction-delay-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，欧盟将于 10 月 4 日投票最终确定对中国制造的电动汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-vote-oct-4-finalize-tariffs-china-made-evs-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-28/</link><description>据彭博社周六援引知情人士消息称，欧盟计划于 10 月 4 日就是否对中国制造的进口电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税进行投票。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 07:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-vote-oct-4-finalize-tariffs-china-made-evs-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚后卫瑟卡蒂因十字韧带受伤缺阵</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-defender-circati-ruled-out-with-cruciate-ligament-injury-2024-09-28/</link><description>澳大利亚后卫亚历山德罗·瑟卡蒂将缺席亚洲世界杯预选赛第三轮的剩余比赛，此前他所在的意甲球队帕尔马宣布他在周五的训练中前十字韧带断裂。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 04:12:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/australia-defender-circati-ruled-out-with-cruciate-ligament-injury-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，道明银行可能在洗钱调查中认罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/td-bank-nears-possible-guilty-plea-money-laundering-probe-wsj-reports-2024-09-28/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周五报道，道明银行即将对其美国零售银行未能遏制与中国犯罪集团和非法芬太尼销售有关的洗钱活动的刑事指控认罪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 04:05:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/td-bank-nears-possible-guilty-plea-money-laundering-probe-wsj-reports-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>中美会谈后在南海举行军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-military-drills-south-china-sea-after-talks-with-us-2024-09-28/</link><description>周六，在中国最高外交官与美国外长讨论缓解地区紧张局势的方法数小时后，中国军方表示，中国空军和海军正在南海争议地区进行演习。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 04:04:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-military-drills-south-china-sea-after-talks-with-us-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国与亚太国家在南海举行联合海上演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-australia-japan-new-zealand-hold-joint-maritime-activity-south-2024-09-28/</link><description>周六，五国武装部队在南海部分海域举行联合海上演习，而中国则在有争议的水道上进行了自己的军事演习。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 01:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-australia-japan-new-zealand-hold-joint-maritime-activity-south-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，币安创始人赵被美国释放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-founder-zhao-released-us-custody-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-27/</link><description>据彭博社援引美国监狱管理局发言人的消息报道，币安创始人赵长鹏已于周五从加州一所惩教所获释。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 22:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-founder-zhao-released-us-custody-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>阿联酋外长表示阿联酋正在加倍加强与美国的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uae-foreign-minister-says-his-country-is-doubling-down-us-ties-2024-09-27/</link><description>海湾国家外交部长周五表示，阿拉伯联合酋长国正在加强与美国的关系，这是在拜登担任总统期间出现几次摩擦点后关系回暖的迹象。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 19:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uae-foreign-minister-says-his-country-is-doubling-down-us-ties-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>与中国会面后，布林肯表示北京关于乌克兰和平的言论“站不住脚”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-chinas-wang-meet-un-sidelines-2024-09-27/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在周五与中国外交部长王毅的会谈中强调了美国对中国支持俄罗斯国防工业基础的强烈担忧，称北京关于乌克兰和平的言论“不合常理”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 17:39:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-chinas-wang-meet-un-sidelines-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管泽连斯基愤怒，中国和巴西仍继续推进乌克兰和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-brazil-press-with-ukraine-peace-plan-despite-zelenskiys-ire-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五，中国和巴西继续努力召集发展中国家支持一项结束俄罗斯乌克兰战争的计划，尽管乌克兰总统泽连斯基否认该倡议符合莫斯科的利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 17:14:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-brazil-press-with-ukraine-peace-plan-despite-zelenskiys-ire-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>禁止中国汽车销售 美国汽车销量每年可能下降 25,000 辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/proposed-biden-chinese-car-tech-ban-could-cut-up-25000-us-auto-sales-2024-09-27/</link><description>美国商务部周五表示，如果禁止连接互联网和关键中国软件和硬件的中国汽车的拟议规则得以实施，美国汽车销量每年可能会减少多达 25,841 辆，而价格则会上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 16:22:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/proposed-biden-chinese-car-tech-ban-could-cut-up-25000-us-auto-sales-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟改变氢能项目拍卖规则以限制中国的存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-changes-hydrogen-project-auction-rules-limit-chinese-presence-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五公布的新条款显示，欧盟宣布修改氢补贴拍卖规则，以限制欧盟在可再生能源供应链中对中国的依赖。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:51:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-changes-hydrogen-project-auction-rules-limit-chinese-presence-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商比亚迪寻求进一步放宽墨西哥电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-byd-seeks-further-easing-mexico-ev-tariffs-local-media-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪正在寻求延长墨西哥政府对电动汽车进口的关税减免，一位高管在周五发表的《改革报》采访中表示，该公司计划在该国建立一家工厂。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:40:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-byd-seeks-further-easing-mexico-ev-tariffs-local-media-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对俄罗斯在中国生产攻击无人机的报道感到担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-concerned-by-report-russia-producing-attack-drones-china-2024-09-27/</link><description>欧盟发言人周五表示，有报道称俄罗斯正在为乌克兰战争开发中国支持的攻击无人机计划，“令人深感担忧”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 13:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-concerned-by-report-russia-producing-attack-drones-china-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国降低短期借贷成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-borrowing-cost-standing-lending-facility-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国央行周五晚间表示，将常备借贷便利（SLF）所有期限的借贷成本降低了 20 个基点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 12:42:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-borrowing-cost-standing-lending-facility-2024-09-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>